  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Last Vanguard</strong> is a <strong>Metroidvania shooter-platformer</strong> with <strong>RPG elements</strong> and <strong>hand-drawn, frame-by-frame animations</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729180/extras/9327aeeb813f5649f817344e30a1e140.poster.avif?t=1760121647\" width=616 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729180/extras/9327aeeb813f5649f817344e30a1e140.webm?t=1760121647\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729180/extras/9327aeeb813f5649f817344e30a1e140.mp4?t=1760121647\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729180/extras/941564fa990786036854680631ee7238.webp?t=1760121647\" width=616 height=49 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore an epic world</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌍 <strong>Explore with freedom</strong> a <strong>stunning hand-crafted world</strong> ravaged by war and ruled by an <strong>evil tyrant</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚔️ <strong>Face a wide variety of enemies</strong> as you <strong>customize your strategy</strong>, <strong>switch weapons</strong>, and <strong>unlock active and passive abilities</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🤝 <strong>Form unexpected alliances</strong> and <strong>discover breathtaking locations</strong> amidst the desolation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729180/extras/25ab940538c09453d6242e6777413635.poster.avif?t=1760121647\" width=616 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729180/extras/25ab940538c09453d6242e6777413635.webm?t=1760121647\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729180/extras/25ab940538c09453d6242e6777413635.mp4?t=1760121647\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729180/extras/941564fa990786036854680631ee7238.webp?t=1760121647\" width=616 height=49 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💀 <strong>28 boss battles</strong> featuring unique <strong>hand-drawn animations</strong> and <strong>varied combat styles</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌎 <strong>9 handcrafted biomes</strong>, each with its own <strong>enemies</strong> and <strong>gameplay mechanics</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔫 <strong>15 types of weapons</strong>, each affecting your <strong>combat style</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ A wide range of <strong>active and passive abilities</strong>, along with different 🪖 <strong>helmets</strong> to personalize your experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧠 <strong>Make your own strategy</strong> by <strong>customizing your equipment</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729180/extras/62e68effaa32fe86009fdaf0a3a48edf.poster.avif?t=1760121647\" width=616 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729180/extras/62e68effaa32fe86009fdaf0a3a48edf.webm?t=1760121647\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729180/extras/62e68effaa32fe86009fdaf0a3a48edf.mp4?t=1760121647\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
